{"title":"Spring boot 修改启动banner内容","date":"2017-12-19T02:21:32.000Z","source":"_posts/2017-12-19.Spring_boot_修改启动banner内容.md","raw":"---\ntitle: Spring boot 修改启动banner内容\ndate: 2017-12-19 10:21:32\ntags: [Spring boot,framework]\n---\n\n我们在启动Spring boot时候会出现以下情况\n\n![banner启动图](http://img.yuekang.org.cn/20171219-102535@2x.png)\n\n我们可以将它改成自己产品的内容修改方式如下\n\n在 src/main/resources/banner.txt 创建并加入内容:\n\n```banner\n\n           _                  \n          (_)                 \n ___  _ __ ___   _____  _ __  \n/ _ \\| '__| \\ \\ / / _ \\| '_ \\\n| (_) | |  | |\\ V / (_) | | | |\n\\___/|_|  |_| \\_/ \\___/|_| |_|\n\n\n${spring-boot.version}${spring-boot.formatted-version}\n```\n\n在banner.txt 文件末尾可以加入`${spring-boot.version}${spring-boot.formatted-version}`用来显示最新的版本等信息\n\n再次启动项目会看到如下结果\n\n![修改后的banner效果图](http://img.yuekang.org.cn/20171219-103130@2x.png)\n\n>每日名言：不要向这个世界认输，因为你还有牛逼的梦想！\n","slug":"2017-12-19-Spring-boot-修改启动banner内容","published":true,"updated":"2024-09-02T09:06:11.422Z","_id":"cm0p37oq90011f8sn5bbkc6fr","comments":true,"layout":"post","photos":[],"html":"<p>我们在启动Spring boot时候会出现以下情况</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.yuekang.org.cn/20171219-102535@2x.png\" alt=\"banner启动图\"></p>\n<p>我们可以将它改成自己产品的内容修改方式如下</p>\n<p>在 src&#x2F;main&#x2F;resources&#x2F;banner.txt 创建并加入内容:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">           _                  </span><br><span class=\"line\">          (_)                 </span><br><span class=\"line\"> ___  _ __ ___   _____  _ __  </span><br><span class=\"line\">/ _ \\| &#x27;__| \\ \\ / 